 Manbij commander Adnan killed in Raqqa offensive|publisher=[[Rudaw Media Network]]|date=30 August 2017}}</ref><br />({{small|[[Manbij Military Council]] general commander}})<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Syrian Democratic Forces.svg}}{{flagicon image|Infobox Manbij Military Council flag.png}} Muhammad Mustafa Ali \"Abu Adel\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://syriadirect.org/news/syrian-democratic-forces-break-through-raqqa-city-limits-for-first-time-capture-neighborhoods/|title=Syrian Democratic Forces break through Raqqa city limits for first time, capture neighborhoods|author1=Mohammad Abdulssattar Ibrahim|author2=Maria Nelson|publisher=Syria Direct|date=6 June 2017|accessdate=7 June 2017}}</ref><br />({{small|Manbij Military Council and Northern Sun Battalion commander}})<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Syrian Democratic Forces.svg}}{{flagicon image|Infobox Manbij Military Council flag.png}} Dilsuz Hashme<ref name=elb>{{cite web|url=https://news.vice.com/story/inside-the-fight-to-retake-raqqa-from-isis|title=Inside The Fight To Retake Raqqa From ISIS|author=[[Aris Roussinos]]|date=19 September 2017}}</ref><br />({{small|Manbij Military Council senior commander}})<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Syrian Democratic Forces.svg}}{{flagicon image|Infobox Manbij Military Council flag.png}} Ibrahim Semho<ref name=elb/><br />({{small|Euphrates Liberation Brigade commander}})<br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Syrian Democratic Forces.svg}}{{flagdeco|Syrian opposition}} Abu Imad<ref name=\"schism\">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-syria-fighters-20170704-story.html|title=A schism among Syrian rebel fighters threatens to slow down the battle against Islamic State|author=Molly Hennessy-Fiske|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|date=4 July 2017|accessdate=6 July 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"joining\">{{cite web|url=http://en.hawarnews.com/the-elite-teams-are-joining-the-wrath-of-euphrates/|title=The Elite Teams are joining the Wrath of Euphrates|publisher=[[Hawar News Agency]]